"""Test for get_elements_from_masking_view."""
masking_view_components = self.utils.get_elements_from_masking_view(self.
    data.smis_mv_1)
self.assertEqual(self.data.m_sg_name, masking_view_components['storagegroup'])
self.assertEqual(self.data.m_portgroup, masking_view_components['portgroup'])
self.assertEqual(self.data.m_initiatorgroup, masking_view_components[
    'initiatorgroup'])
mock.patch.object(provisioning.ProvisioningFunctions, 'get_masking_view',
    return_value={'portGroupId': pcd.CommonData.m_portgroup, 'hostId': pcd.
    CommonData.m_initiatorgroup, 'storageGroupId': pcd.CommonData.m_sg_name})
